					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>If adding a disclosure in this situation is a legal issue, then I can see some reason why people would get up in arms. If its a matter of preference though, then why does it matter if she adds a disclosure? It doesn&#8217;t cost the people who click those affiliate links anything.</p>
